user_query: I'm interested in the latest trends on TikTok. Can you help me search for popular hashtags? Provide me with the view counts of the top 10 hashtags. Additionally, fetch a random quote from the 'funny' category.

TaskList.description: Search for the latest popular hashtags on TikTok.
Fetch view counts for the top 10 popular hashtags retrieved from step 1.
Fetch a random quote from the 'funny' category.
